  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "- The primary purpose is to detect exceptions within instrumentations. Since LLM providers frequently update their APIs, this helps us quickly identify and fix any breaking changes.\n- We only collect anonymous data, with no personally identifiable information. You can view exactly what data we collect in our [Privacy documentation](https://www.traceloop.com/docs/openllmetry/privacy/telemetry).\n- Telemetry is only collected in the SDK. If you use the instrumentations directly without the SDK, no telemetry is collected.",
